    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Certain upper floor rooms in Medieval houses that are smaller than halls and reserved for private family use. The form grew out of the Greek and Roman "solariums (building spaces)."</Note_Text>
